Overlord Raising Hell Trainer by CALIBER
Launch the trainer first, then launch the Game and then Press F1 at the Main Menu.
Numpad 1: Set 10,000 Life and increase Life Max
Numpad 5: Toggle One-Hit Kills by Overlord On/Off
Numpad 6: Convert Overlord from Good to Evil and Back.
Numpad 7: Save Current Position for Teleport
Numpad 8: Teleport Back To Saved Position
Numpad 9: Go back to position before Teleport
Numpad 1- this will reset sometimes between teleports, cutscenes, and after Auto
Saves.  You can see that the bar increases when it is activated so take
note to see that it is still activated after certain events.
Numpad 2- same as health.  take note that the bar has elongated.
Numpad 3- this will max your gold to 1,000,000
Numpad 4- this increases the minion cap to an incredible 10,000 units.  You can go
to the dungeon and kill certain creatures to increase your minions quickly
and easily.  A very powerful option!
Numpad 5- This toggles off and on the One-Hit kills.  This option only affects the
attack of the Overlord himself.  Your minions are not affected.  For instance
the Troll is nearly times as powerful as you, but you can strike it dead with
Numpad 6- this toggles your character from good to evil, changes costumes, etc.
Numpad 7- this will save your current position for when you engage teleport
Numpad 8- this will activate the teleport and send you to the position you saved previously
Numpad 9- if you didn't mean to teleport or want to go back to the previous position before
the teleport, this will teleport you back to the position you were in before
Numpad +(plus)- this will hover you 3 meters in the air.  Each time you press it, you will go
higher.  As long as you do not try to walk you will remain in hover mode.  You
can direct your minions from the air if you desire.  Also, if you haven't gone
too high, you can cast spells, especially the fireball, at targets.  Most
attacks are useless while you are in the air.
Numpad -(minus)- your minions are impervious to attacks.  Certain things may kill them but they
seem to be invincible to all that i tested.  Have fun with them!  Build your army!
Note: This trainer is compatible with our Trainer Customizer.  Click the Troubleshooting
